#. from the basin of Mexico.
#. TRANSLATORS: https://iau.org/news/pressreleases/detail/iau1912/
msgid "Axólotl"
msgstr ""

#. TRANSLATORS: Proper name of star HD 7199
#. TRANSLATORS: Emiw represents love in the local Makhuwa language of the
